{"tid":1674154,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"華春瑩撐林鄭言論「被消失」 四中全會前夕不尋常","createTime":"2019-10-25T04:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T10:03:01.000Z","uid":212626,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"dda56dc7c93f9d6ddaf527857822667244ef0516","tid":1674154,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T04:54:48.000Z","msg":"英國《#金融時報》（FT）周三報道，北京計劃於明年3月更換香港特首 #林鄭月娥，中國外交部發言人華春瑩其後在例行新聞發布會上指有關報道是<span style=\"color: red;\">「別有用心的政治謠言」</span>，以一貫口吻強調中央政府堅定支持林鄭，內地網站亦廣泛轉載。不過，中國外交部的官方文字紀錄未幾已經不見了華春瑩這段相關說法。<br />\n<br />\n#華春瑩 就《金融時報》報道的回應，外交部在周三當日把全數文字紀錄發放予本港媒體，<span style=\"color: red;\">但不到24小時，其官方網站上相關的闢謠回應忽然「被消失」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，本來很多內地網站周三全面轉載華春瑩「別有用心的 #政治謠言」的官方口徑，後來都一概刪掉。消息人士透露，外交部以往也曾經在記者會後就敏感議題更改用字，甚至整段刪除。<br />\n<br />\n由於事件正值 #四中全會 前夕，不少網民認為外交部今次做法頗不尋常，揣測是否代表中央態度有變，亦有網民揣測可能是華春瑩發言不當，唯有抽起這段文字。<br />\n<br />\n與其他外交部發言人相比，華春瑩較多出現臨時「爆肚」情況，故未能確定真正原因是否與中央立場有關。<br />\n<br />\n「反修例風暴」新聞專題 深入分析 <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2l1PLjs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2l1PLjs&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTfzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=b1b825be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">bit.ly/2l1PLjs</a><br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n#信報 #今日信報 #撤換特首 #華春瑩言論 #被消失 #不尋常<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/139543009419663/posts/3474126755961255/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F139543009419663%2Fposts%2F3474126755961255%2F&d=r5q0VKZH5TKX5M4XK8oFTfzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=75a5e7a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/139543009419663/posts/3474126755961255/</a>"},{"pid":"ae89744dc39db6df3c721de6d798dac6b90ba76d","tid":1674154,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T04:56:49.000Z","msg":"爆肚咁串<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57829203951ad7a4a08ea66f85c8703f54574695","tid":1674154,"uid":92908,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T04:58:54.000Z","msg":"華春瑩先唔怕<br />\n一張機票到美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50a2ad008554460b6972cf01f257d2f72f41828","tid":1674154,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T04:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b8d00c280b77b795420729fe538522ea161a7cd","tid":1674154,"uid":3677,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:00:26.000Z","msg":"依家響地牢到俾集大大屌緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c6969db5803c8327384720341ecfc67f6fe060","tid":1674154,"uid":238101,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />落地獄啦林鄭"},{"pid":"24a3de50b814d4ca98c953c5e3cc4e58fd0bacb1","tid":1674154,"uid":235015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:02:16.000Z","msg":"殺人犯大清算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1017cc2a1065eb52229070d001f7cd5a92fbc8","tid":1674154,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:04:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a11607668d6e5091c1d8332ab1e2b1ba7a645c","tid":1674154,"uid":286309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:05:28.000Z","msg":"爆肚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n揸綠卡係唔同啲嘅"},{"pid":"97b3753be0380c0d0460249127b279485a443b8b","tid":1674154,"uid":193215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T05:05:44.000Z","msg":"可以爆肚㗎咩大劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal